name: Structure
description: Generates a structural frame from a set of Levels and an Envelope.

Grid X-Axis Interval.description: Grix interval in the X direction.

Grid Y-Axis Interval.description: Grid interval in the Y direction.

Slab Edge Offset.description: The offset of the grid lines from the slab edge.

Display Grid.description: Display the grid on the ground plane?

Column Type.description: The wide flange section shape to use for all columns.

Girder Type.description: The wide flange section shape to use for all girders.

Beam Type.description: The wide flange section shape to use for all beams.

Create Beams On First Level.description: Should beams be created at the lowest level of the structure?

Slab Thickness.description: The slab thickness. Control the offset of the structure from a level.

Insert Columns At External Edges.description: Should columns be created at external locations?
